<plot>A film essay on Ulla Neuerburg, a theater director from Germany, reflecting her work and living in the USA. The visual track of this film was shot in Iceland and in New York City. Formally it's an essay on how sight and sound can influence perception when they are separate from each other.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?393482</url></doc>
